# Secrets / environment-specific config
# The plist holds Supabase URL/anon key + Google client ID. Anon keys are
# safe to ship in clients (paired with RLS), but we keep environment config
# out of the repo so Debug/Staging/Prod builds can swap it cleanly. Use
# Centmond.plist.example as a template.
Centmond/Centmond.plist
